{"id":294507,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/维权网-只缘拆迁安置谈判起争议，芜湖官员当街/","date":"2013-05-21T10:16:44Z","modified":"2013-05-21T10:16:44Z","title":"维权网 | 只缘拆迁安置谈判起争议，芜湖官员当街殴打弱女子（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div align=\"left\"><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>（维权网信息员张宁宁报道）</span>2013</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span>日<span>下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>点左右，周琛应约到镜湖区政府内与王慧山区长、征收办周炳主任等商谈拆迁安置问题。芜湖弱女子周琛遭遇强拆前的房屋面临大街，位于芜湖市黄金地段，即使按照</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2009</span><span>年芜湖市拆迁安置政策，其门面房价拆迁价达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7023</span><span>元</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span><span>平米。原先，政府官员同意以</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">09</span><span>年门面房的市场价结算。不知何故，政府官员出尔反尔，仅以</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3181</span><span>元</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span><span>平米结账，还不到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">09</span><span>年房屋市场价的一半。周琛难以接受，双方不欢而散。</span></p>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>已经是晚上<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span>点多了，周琛早已饥肠辘辘，离开镜湖区政府，赶到大润发超市准备买食品充饥，偶然遇到一个朋友，就与其聊天。恰巧征收办周炳主任也在超市买包子，从周琛面前经过。周琛向他打招呼，并且希望政府官员体恤民情，合理安置，不要违背拆迁政策。他们一路走，一路争论。一直走到镜湖区法院大门前。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>征收办主任周炳说，我就是政策。周琛说，你就是政策，你就可以翻手为云覆手为雨吗？征收办主任周炳恼羞成怒，猛地给周琛一拳，正打在周琛的眼睛上。周琛忍着疼痛，就地反击。怎奈一个弱女子如何打得过一个大男子。周琛呼救，因天已晚，无人发现。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>周琛觉得眼睛疼痛难忍，要去医院治疗。奇怪的是，征收办主任周炳阻挡周琛去看病，竟向<span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span>报警，还打电话给政法委求援。<span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span>民警赶到现场，将周琛带到北京路派出所做笔录。做笔录的民警叫计辉，他翘的二郎腿，抽着烟，喝着茶，几乎在欣赏一个受伤的猎物。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></p>\n<p></span></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-OxYCtMvsZWA/UZsyxVneXdI/AAAAAAAAiU4/HVbHQ8Aq9rQ/s1600/%E5%BC%B1%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E5%91%A8%E7%90%9B%E7%9C%BC%E7%9D%9B%E8%A2%AB%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%AE%98%E5%91%98%E6%89%93%E8%82%BF.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-OxYCtMvsZWA/UZsyxVneXdI/AAAAAAAAiU4/HVbHQ8Aq9rQ/s320/%E5%BC%B1%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E5%91%A8%E7%90%9B%E7%9C%BC%E7%9D%9B%E8%A2%AB%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%AE%98%E5%91%98%E6%89%93%E8%82%BF.jpg\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-x-XfDQrlthM/UZsy7GmLn8I/AAAAAAAAiVI/WVHvuLOuyHs/s1600/W501Q0UQC152~1OHG37Z%7D7R.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-x-XfDQrlthM/UZsy7GmLn8I/AAAAAAAAiVI/WVHvuLOuyHs/s320/W501Q0UQC152~1OHG37Z%7D7R.jpg\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-77fQbEZ9WHc/UZszF4I0oqI/AAAAAAAAiVQ/j6DxH71x8B0/s1600/%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%9C%AA%E7%A9%BF%E8%AD%A6%E6%9C%8D%E6%B0%91%E8%AD%A6%E7%BF%98%E7%9D%80%E4%BA%8C%E9%83%8E%E8%85%BF%E5%9C%A8%E5%81%9A%E7%AC%94%E5%BD%95.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-77fQbEZ9WHc/UZszF4I0oqI/AAAAAAAAiVQ/j6DxH71x8B0/s320/%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%9C%AA%E7%A9%BF%E8%AD%A6%E6%9C%8D%E6%B0%91%E8%AD%A6%E7%BF%98%E7%9D%80%E4%BA%8C%E9%83%8E%E8%85%BF%E5%9C%A8%E5%81%9A%E7%AC%94%E5%BD%95.jpg\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-WBnNINQuzRI/UZszH_1_e3I/AAAAAAAAiVY/mIzPaGsEaTw/s1600/%E5%91%A8%E7%90%9B%E8%A2%AB%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%AE%98%E5%91%98%E6%AE%B4%E6%89%93%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%98%E8%A2%AB%E6%8A%BC%E5%BE%80%E6%B4%BE%E5%87%BA%E6%89%80%E8%AF%A2%E9%97%AE.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-WBnNINQuzRI/UZszH_1_e3I/AAAAAAAAiVY/mIzPaGsEaTw/s320/%E5%91%A8%E7%90%9B%E8%A2%AB%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%AE%98%E5%91%98%E6%AE%B4%E6%89%93%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%98%E8%A2%AB%E6%8A%BC%E5%BE%80%E6%B4%BE%E5%87%BA%E6%89%80%E8%AF%A2%E9%97%AE.jpg\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><smal